  <title>Cam-Follower</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Cam-Follower Shapes<keyword>Flat-faced Cam Follower</keyword><keyword>General Shape</keyword><keyword>Knife-Edged Cam Follower</keyword><keyword>Round Cam Follower</keyword><keyword>Straight Cam Follower</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="6" colcount="2" style="cell-padding:0px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower Shapes</text><text style="font-weight:normal;"> (See</text> also <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Cam-Follower-Motion" styleclass="Popup Box2">Cam-Follower Motions</link>)</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower</text> is the shape that is in continuous contact with the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower</text> is a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Sketch-Loop" styleclass="Popup Box2">sketch-loop</link> with a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Profile-Element" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Profile</link> / <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Extrusion</text>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower Shapes</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:89px;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-CircularCamFollower-Ex-Pop.ipp" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">1: Circular Cam-Follower </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Popup Box">A</text>&#32;<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Sketch-Element-Circle" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Circle</link> in the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">This represents a Bearing or Pin that is a Cylindrical, or Crown/Barrel shaped. It is the most common shape for a Cam-Follower.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:89px;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-FlatFacedFollower-Ex-pop.ipp" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">2: Flat-faced Follower </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Usually, 4×<text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Lines</text> as a sketch of a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">long</text> rectangle.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The <text styleclass="VariableName-small">rectangle</text> must be long enough so that the Cam</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Follower is always in contact with the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:89px;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-ContourCamFollower-Ex-Pop.ipp" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">3: Multi-Contour Cam-Follower </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">For example, four Arcs, with Tangent constraints,</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">oined as an ellipse.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:89px;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-KnifeEdged-CamFollower-Ex-pop.ipp" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">4: Knife-Edged Cam-Follower</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">An <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">arc</text>,with a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">small</text> radius. Merge the <text styleclass="Element">ARC</text> with other sketch-elements</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The small <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Arc</text> represent the knife-edge.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A true knife-edge is practically not possible. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
